{"id":141236,"date":[{"year":1947,"month":3,"day":17}],"page":"6","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"380","ytitle":"","mtitle":"夜祷","ftitle":"诗画","authors":["柳青"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"柳青"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜，正如“紫罗兰”色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么肃穆壮丽!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在顶上，高高地挂起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星星，又如圣殿里的烛焰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么晶萤地摇曳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在每一边没空地点起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群山，有如那高耸的圆柱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站立在这幽静底草地；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样，我踯躅于礼拜堂里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"偏地蠕动着是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上帝底儿女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屏息而微静吟着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虔诚且热望底祷音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喃喃地:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耶华华敬爱底主呀!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你底儿女"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生长在这悲悯底世纪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白鸽已飞向枪炮口儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吻着血红底火焰，且那么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲切恋依?!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们囚在这黑夜里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"削下血肉来填筑着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这为酷争底战地!!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，听到了——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘶哑了底哀赞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是发自每一个饿僵了底"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人儿底喉底!!!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这该是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们唱出底赞美诗?!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，上帝!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们只有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手托着自己底头颅!!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跪在殿前，敬献还你!!!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这么黝黑底夜里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已遮盖了人间血泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"染红了山河延遍了的大地!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杀声，已湮没了祷求底诚语!!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自由底花儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早已残葬于"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏烂了底足印里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粉碎了尸体!!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵!这么漫长而漫长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"且多么悲怆底夜里!!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟至何时!?何时!!!!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1947\\03\\473h060501.JPG\">"}]}